</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1363,1531]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">
Twenty five species are placed in this genus (Mound 
<number box="[756,816,1363,1387]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" value="2012.0">2012</number>
), however specimens are not known for many of these names (
<bibRefCitation author="Hoddle" box="[237,453,1399,1423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" refString="Hoddle, M. S., Mound, L. A. &amp; Paris, D. (2012) Thrips of California 2012. Available: http: // keys. lucidcentral. org / keys / v 3 / thrips _ of _ california / Thrips _ of _ California. html (accessed 10. x. 2012)." type="journal article" year="2012">
Hoddle 
<emphasis box="[329,377,1399,1423]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">et al</emphasis>
. 
<number box="[392,453,1399,1423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" value="2012.0">2012</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[502,550,1400,1423]" name="Iran" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">Iran</collectingCountry>
, only 
<taxonomicName authority="Haliday" authorityName="Haliday" box="[619,851,1399,1423]" class="Insecta" family="Phlaeothripidae" genus="Phlaeothrips" kingdom="Animalia" order="Thysanoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coriaceus">
<emphasis box="[619,755,1400,1423]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">P. coriaceus</emphasis>
Haliday
</taxonomicName>
has been recorded (zur Strssen 
<number box="[1208,1268,1399,1423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" value="2003.0">2003</number>
), based on two females beaten from shrubs by W. Wittmer in 
<number box="[698,757,1435,1459]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" value="1970.0">1970</number>
. In addition to 
<collectingCountry box="[941,989,1436,1459]" name="Iran" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">Iran</collectingCountry>
, the species is recorded widely across Europe (
<bibRefCitation author="Priesner" box="[249,411,1471,1495]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" refString="Priesner, H. (1964) Ordnung Thysanoptera (Fransenflugler, Thripse). In: Franz, H. (Ed.), Bestimmungsbucher zur Bodenfauna Europas 2, 1 - 242. Akademie-Verlag." type="journal article" year="1964">
Priesner 
<number box="[354,411,1471,1495]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" value="1964.0">1964</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) and also in California (
<bibRefCitation author="Hoddle" box="[699,924,1471,1495]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" refString="Hoddle, M. S., Mound, L. A. &amp; Paris, D. (2012) Thrips of California 2012. Available: http: // keys. lucidcentral. org / keys / v 3 / thrips _ of _ california / Thrips _ of _ California. html (accessed 10. x. 2012)." type="journal article" year="2012">
Hoddle 
<emphasis box="[794,845,1471,1495]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="284">et al</emphasis>
. 
<number box="[863,924,1471,1495]" pageId="5" pageNumber="284" value="2012.0">2012</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). No specimens have been examined by the present author.
</paragraph>
